## Prometheus Metric Types üìä

**Counter** - Only goes up (resets on restart)
```go
http_requests_total
errors_total
```

**Gauge** - Goes up and down
```go
temperature_celsius
memory_usage_bytes
concurrent_connections
```

**Histogram** - Buckets of observations
```go
http_request_duration_seconds
```


