## Creating Metrics with Labels

```go
// house/awair/awair.go
m.Temp = prometheus.NewGaugeVec(prometheus.GaugeOpts{
    Namespace: "awair",
    Name:      "temperature_celcius",
    Help:      "Temperature",
}, []string{"location"})  // Label for different rooms!

m.CO2 = prometheus.NewGaugeVec(prometheus.GaugeOpts{
    Namespace: "awair",
    Name:      "CO2",
    Help:      "CO2 ppm",
}, []string{"location"})
```

